"sable" is a Python package for converting text to speech using Amazon Polly.

The following example converts the contents of the "terminal contents" section above to speech.

import sable

# Create a SableMark object from the text.
sableMark = sable.SableMark(text)

# Create a Sable object from the SableMark object.
sable = sable.Sable(sableMark)

